@startuml
title Client DB Surface (After)
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam ArrowColor #111111
skinparam defaultFontColor #111111
skinparam defaultFontName Consolas

actor "SDK Consumer" as Consumer #D6EAF8
component "createClient(...)" as Client #D5F5E3
component "Root methods\nfrom / rpc / query" as RootApi #FCF3CF
component "db module namespace\nfrom/select/insert/upsert/update/delete/rpc/query" as DbModule #F9E79F
component "TableQueryBuilder" as TableBuilder #FADBD8
component "Gateway HTTP Client" as Gateway #E8DAEF

Consumer --> Client : build client
Client --> RootApi : preserve existing API
Client --> DbModule : add namespaced API

Consumer --> RootApi : existing calls remain valid
Consumer --> DbModule : new namespaced db calls

DbModule --> RootApi : proxy core operations
RootApi --> TableBuilder : from(table)
TableBuilder --> Gateway : execute fetch/insert/update/delete/query/rpc
RootApi --> Gateway : query/rpc direct

note right of DbModule
Backwards-compatible expansion seam
for future database-specific APIs.
end note
@enduml
